title: Bryn Mawr Upper Level Duplex, Hardwood Floors, Video Walkthrough
posting_body: ['Bryn Mawr Upper Level Duplex, Hardwood Floors, Sun Room, Video Tour', 'Property Address', '404 Sheridan Ave S - #2 | Minneapolis, MN 55405', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'This unit is available for in person showings.', 'The unit is in great condition and will have a full repaint before move in.', 'Move in dates for Aug 1st through 9-1.', 'The video walk through and photos are of the unit as it is now.', 'The home is in great shape and located in a wonderful neighborhood.', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Laundry shared in the basement.', 'Lawn taken care of by the owner.', 'Radiator heating and window unit AC.', 'Tenant responsible for Gas/Electric, and Snow Removal.', 'Pets are welcome with positive rental reference and credit.', '(Dog fee $30mo, Cat fee $20mo)', 'Applications are available on the Guardian Property Management website.', 'Each application is $50 per adult and can be paid with a credit or debit card.', 'Application is based on income, credit history (Guardian Property Management will not use credit score but will be using information from your credit report), rental/work history and includes a criminal background check.', 'For full criteria visit our website and click “apply now” on the listed unit.', 'Any additional questions please call or email Billy.', 'Broker: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Agent:', 'Billy Sommers', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,150', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,849.00', 'Available: Now', 'Security Deposit: $1,849.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
